    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >From the creator of <strong>Who's Lila?</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Last Look along Woodward Boulevard is an esoteric horror puzzle adventure, where your <strong>thoughts and mood</strong> affect the environment around you. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144810/extras/3d790e22542f78e308417c9d080bc1e4.poster.avif?t=1752837217\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144810/extras/3d790e22542f78e308417c9d080bc1e4.webm?t=1752837217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144810/extras/3d790e22542f78e308417c9d080bc1e4.mp4?t=1752837217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through strangest planes, constantly struggling to keep your own mind in check, solve puzzles <strong>by using your mood</strong> and avoid the many dangers awaiting you along the road.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Who deterred you from your path? Who is the mysterious person guiding you? Why does this all seem so familiar...</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144810/extras/0c3abf172fdd6a980d4fdaa1220ab1e1.poster.avif?t=1752837217\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144810/extras/0c3abf172fdd6a980d4fdaa1220ab1e1.webm?t=1752837217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144810/extras/0c3abf172fdd6a980d4fdaa1220ab1e1.mp4?t=1752837217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Thought/Mood system - hard to control at first; As you move through the journey, you will gain access to more and more tools to wrangle your thoughts. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Gritty dithered style, now in multicolor! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > More focus on puzzles and mechanics tied to mood</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Live action cutscenes with some familiar faces</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Surreal and diverse locations </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more..</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144810/extras/615869a5fba957bf97a434a0253bc803.poster.avif?t=1752837217\" width=616 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144810/extras/615869a5fba957bf97a434a0253bc803.webm?t=1752837217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2144810/extras/615869a5fba957bf97a434a0253bc803.mp4?t=1752837217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
